race.comment: THIS BLACK DUCK (3) is a consistent type who is lining up for his first start here. Was an all the way winner latest, running away with a 2 length win at Bendigo (23.88). Can measure up again. PAW MANTRA (2) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 2.25 lengths at Warragul in a handy 25.96 beating Paw Razor. One of the leading chances again. TAKE THE EDGE (1) is a fast beginner who has shown good improvement at her last two starts, rewarded with a win last time at Warragul over 400m. The form from her last run stacks up well. Expected to measure up again. MIGHTY SCAR (7) defied the market to win last start and cannot be ruled out.
